      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. When you mention the north-south divide and those ethnic blocs, do you see much actual stability there? Or is it mostly just a constant cycle of these groups clashing over land and power? Like, is there a specific way these groups tend to behave when tensions rise?",
